"Extreme Eradication III":
"My requests from here on out won't be getting any
easier. Just turn around and walk the other way if you
don't think you can handle it. I want you to annihilate
en masse the D-arkers that are spawned, but they
have to be tougher than the ones you fought before.
You choose where. This shouldn't be impossible for
you, based on your performance so far, but I can't
really recommend that you actually do it.
Think carefully, now.
*Target: Hostiles level 34 or higher"
"マイルドマイルド・マーダー・Ⅲ"

"さて、ここからは軽くじゃすまない
依頼内容になっていくよ。
その気がないのならＵターンだ。
場所は問わない。
より強力な敵の出現する状況下で
生産されたダーカーの一斉殲滅だ。
あんたの力なら不可能じゃないだろうけど
おすすめはしないよ。よく考えな。

※Lv.34～のエネミーが対象"
